pub struct User {

    age: i32,
    active: bool,
}

    #[primary_key]
    id: i32,
    title: String,
    price: f32,
    in_stock: bool,
}

#[table(name = note)]
pub struct Note {
    #[primary_key]
    id: i32,
    body: String,
    rating: i64,
    pinned: bool,
}

}

}

    #[primary_key]

    pub body: String,
    pub rating: i64,

}
